reviewText:
I sent this movie (Zorro's Fighting Legion), back as it was not the one I requested. I ordered "Zorro Rides Again" and I haven't heard if you got it back yet or that you will exchange or any word at all. Could you let me know what is happening please?
  Thank You  Dennis Snider
For anybody who love series movies this one is for you its got alot of action and adverture.
